OL,8,GStories shape the future. The stories
OL,9,Gwe grow up with influence what we
OL,10,Gbelieve is possible, who we think
OL,11,Gwe’re allowed to become, and what kind
OL,12,Gof world we imagine ourselves living
OL,13,Gin. But storytelling isn’t limited to
OL,14,Gbooks, films, or television. Every
OL,15,Ginterface tells a story. Every layout
OL,16,Gnudges human behaviour. Every hack
OL,17,Gprovokes a reaction. Everything we
OL,18,Gbuild changes the way people
OL,19,Gexperience the world around them. This
OL,20,Gtalk explores the hidden power of
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
